Package: newpost
Title: Create a new index.qmd file for your Quarto blog
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Sharon", "Machlis", , "sharon@kc1yr.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simple and somewhat crude package with one function and one RStudio add-in to create a new folder in your posts directory with the post headline, create an index.qmd file, and add simple YAML.
